sentences: Dennis Latos (born March 11, 1992) is an American film director, producer and editor.
Dennis directed, produced, and edited the short film, Leylak, which held its world premiere at the 20th Annual Tribeca Film Festival in June 2021 and was awarded a Special Jury Prize for the film.
During his senior year, Latos was accepted to New York University's Tisch School of the Arts Summer Program in Dublin, Ireland.
